  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The International Monetary Fund reaffirmed its commitment to support Sri Lanka",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "We hope that the political crisis in Sri Lanka will be resolved. The International Monetary Fund has expressed its hope that this resolution will lead to the resumption of discussions on aid programs for Sri Lanka.",
        "Following the massive demonstration in Colombo demanding the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa, the President has announced that he will resign on the 13th. This is what the International Monetary Fund has said.",
        "It said that it is closely observing the developments in Sri Lanka and hopes that the current political change will lead to the resumption of negotiations regarding the program with the support of the International Monetary Fund.",
        "'Due to the impact of the current economic crisis, we are concerned about the people, especially the poor. And we reaffirm our commitment to support Sri Lanka in accordance with IMF policies at this difficult time,\" the IMF said.",
        "The IMF also said it will continue technical discussions with officials at the Ministry of Finance and the Central Bank of Sri Lanka. In this case, it is essential that there is a government in the country for decisive discussions to be carried out with the International Monetary Fund. It is noteworthy that Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has said that it would be wrong to lead the country without the administration of a government."
      ],
